Name:             HAppS-Extra
Version:          0.6
License:          BSD3
Author:           jeremy@n-heptane.com
Maintainer:       jeremy@n-heptane.com

Synopsis:         Components built on top of HAppS+HSP
Description:      A collection of components built on top of HAppS+HSP, including
                  Google Analytics, a Calendar widget, and more.

Hs-Source-Dirs:   src
Exposed-Modules:  HSP.Google.Analytics, HSP.HTML.Extra, HAppS.Extra, HAppS.Data.IxSet.Extra, HAppS.Data.User.Password,
		  HAppS.Data.Session, HAppS.State.Extra, HAppS.Data.Account
                  
Build-Depends:    base, hsp >= 0.4.4, harp >= 0.4, HAppS-IxSet, HAppS-Data, HAppS-Util, mtl, random, HAppS-State
Build-Type:       Simple
Category:         Web, Language

Extensions:             MultiParamTypeClasses,
                        TypeFamilies,
                        FlexibleContexts,
                        FlexibleInstances,
                        TypeSynonymInstances,
                        OverlappingInstances,
                        UndecidableInstances
